<text top="449" left="975" width="1219" height="96" font="font6" id="p1_t8" reading_order_no="3" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">quarters  of  a  washed-up  ex-superhero </text>
<text top="531" left="975" width="1221" height="96" font="font5" id="p1_t9" reading_order_no="4" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">called  Nite  Owl.  It’s  adamp,  vaulted </text>
<text top="612" left="974" width="1236" height="96" font="font5" id="p1_t10" reading_order_no="5" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">space  packed  with  avian-themed  cos- </text>
<text top="694" left="969" width="1241" height="95" font="font5" id="p1_t11" reading_order_no="6" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">tumes  and  machine  tools,  a  boys’-own- </text>
<text top="774" left="972" width="1220" height="98" font="font6" id="p1_t12" reading_order_no="7" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">adventure  clubhouse.  At  its  center  is  the </text>
<text top="856" left="973" width="1221" height="97" font="font6" id="p1_t13" reading_order_no="8" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">Owlship—a  UFO-looking  aircraft  with </text>
<text top="936" left="968" width="1227" height="98" font="font7" id="p1_t14" reading_order_no="9" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">two  round  windows  that  look  like  big </text>
<text top="1019" left="972" width="1229" height="96" font="font5" id="p1_t15" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">shiny  eyes.  1And  here,  ona  Vancouver </text>
<text top="1100" left="973" width="1218" height="97" font="font6" id="p1_t16" reading_order_no="11" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">soundstage,  Nite  Owl’s  legendary lair  has </text>
<text top="1181" left="969" width="1222" height="98" font="font6" id="p1_t17" reading_order_no="12" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">been  brought  to  real  life.  The  Owlship  is </text>
<text top="1264" left="967" width="1240" height="94" font="font5" id="p1_t18" reading_order_no="13" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">the  size  of  an  Escalade,  and  I’m  stand- </text>
<text top="1342" left="968" width="1233" height="100" font="font8" id="p1_t19" reading_order_no="14" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">ing  inside.  I’ll  admit  it:  I’m  surprised. </text>
<text top="1656" left="668" width="914" height="41" font="font9" id="p1_t20" reading_order_no="15" segment_no="12" tag_type="text">THE  GODLIKE  DR.  MANHATTAN  IS  JUST  ONE  OF  THE  DYNAMIC </text>
